<div dir="ltr">Hi again everyone,
<div><br>
</div>
<div>I would like to clarify two things:</div>
<div>1. JPIC only reimburses electronic components up to 50 RMB.<br>
</div>
<div>2. I understand many of the groups had spent a fortune in materials for the exterior design (e.g. chassis, mechanical parts, etc.). While we cannot reimburse such expense, it is important that you minimise the cost of prototype - e.g. by using recycled
 materials and/or cost-effective design. I will require all groups to estimate the overall cost in manufacturing your product in your report. You will be scored based on the cost effectiveness.</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>Thanks for all questions to Andy and me so far. We are always happy to take any of your enquiries, whenever you are not clear about the design &amp; build project!</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>Regards,</div>
<div>Matthew</div>
